{"tid":670380,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"幾時有人教班無知婦孺擔遮係遮唔撚到太陽","createTime":"2018-05-19T10:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T13:34:02.000Z","uid":181238,"like":3,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e449e12e00dde810517432c6f91b021018d4a8ce","tid":670380,"uid":181238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T10:10:27.000Z","msg":"我dllm條街已經好撚窄<br />\n人已經好撚多<br />\n落雨我唔怪你<br />\n你擔住把遮一個人霸三個人位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有d仲要一路擔一路行一路玩手機<br />\n成日遮車埋其他人度<br />\n身手冇咁敏捷都畀你插盲<br />\n<br />\n再講<br />\n你地班c9港女最怕嘅紫外線<br />\n唔撚係由上而下咁落嚟㗎on9<br />\n地下彈返上嚟嗰d仲甘<br />\n你前面後面左面右面全部都曬撚住你<br />\n你擋上面有撚用呀？<br />\n如果唔係d鬼婆做乜要去沙灘曬<br />\n係d沙反射上嚟曬d均勻d嘛（呢d係中三物理）<br />\n<br />\ndllm你貪靚你搽防曬/由頭包到腳趾尾冇人鬧你<br />\n擔遮真係好撚阻街好撚樣衰好撚無知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1377cdcca4800da21d5ff110f73474827f1fb4f8","tid":670380,"uid":30404,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T10:13:20.000Z","msg":"你唔俾人哋把遮防UV?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebb556fc2baa60d034c626730c33df788e3cbe89","tid":670380,"uid":144211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1377cdcca4800da21d5ff110f73474827f1fb4f8","tid":670380,"uid":30404,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T10:13:20.000Z","msg":"你唔俾人哋把遮防UV?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T10:14:37.000Z","msg":"睇過啦，盲"},{"pid":"080f4692ba2c3788370f841bdbd35ccde2ad3e27","tid":670380,"uid":30856,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1377cdcca4800da21d5ff110f73474827f1fb4f8","tid":670380,"uid":30404,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T10:13:20.000Z","msg":"你唔俾人哋把遮防UV?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T10:15:00.000Z","msg":"睇字啦"},{"pid":"dc6c4765bdefd5af6c73b05800aae9349d75398a","tid":670380,