b99c3f89a0e919cf5627aecbdc","tid":670380,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e29ab9f86df2c45ab2a1069f4f9e9af8e892aca","tid":670380,"uid":181238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2e2e604ba1eddfeb86110b40a12a19e3849867d","tid":670380,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T10:39:34.000Z","msg":"擔遮有咩問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T10:47:06.000Z","msg":"寫左，你盲？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T11:16:16.000Z","msg":"你冇寫擔遮有咩問題，你只係話把遮霸住條街，但其實係人太多、路太窄嘅問題，得閒去睇下電視。<br />\n另外你話d人把遮傷到人，係d人粗心大意嘅問題。<br />\n所以你控訴嘅問題都唔係針對擔遮此一行為。"},{"pid":"242bfc378734c5495db37dfb4b0f07b09dfb690d","tid":670380,"uid":86434,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T11:52:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你都on撚9 紫外線地面反射番上去得果10%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋唔止紫外線 部份可視光、紅外線都有害<br />\n<br />\n讀得書少唔識就唔好扮識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>反射幾多<br />\n咁就要睇你嗰下地下係乜嘢地喇<br />\n沙地？石屎地？草地？泥地？<br />\n你又可以一口咬定10%嘅<br />\n<br />\n就當真係10%<br />\n仲有你附近d嘢<br />\nd車呀建築物呀泥呀沙呀水呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你咪擔遮囉<br />\n<br />\n我冇話淨係得uv有害<br />\n但d師奶港女的確淨係識uv</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">concrete reflect about 8%-12% and asphalt about 4%-8%. </span>  Even soil reflects between 4%-6% and grass about 2%-5%.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.uvdaily.com.au/blog/reflected-uv/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uvdaily.com.au%2Fblog%2Freflected-uv%2F&d=i4R458lrHm%2FInVyxz36gUNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=2e2e1512\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.uvdaily.com.au/blog/reflected-uv/</a><br />\n<br />\n就算塗滿白色嘅建築物係20% 呢啲google下就搵到 <br />\n城市你同我講有水 邊個會係水入面擔遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n你自己行上街問下擔遮嘅師奶港女<br />\n係因為曬 燦眼先擔遮 定係因為防UV<br />\n<br />\n邏輯真係&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪死雞撐飯蓋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a907f9cf60c69cc5a5023ab909a68606989e1e83","tid":670380,"uid":65858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"242bfc378734c5495db37dfb4b0f07b09dfb690d","tid":670380,"uid":86434,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T11:52:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你都on撚9 紫外線地面反射番上去得果10%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋唔止紫外線 部份可視光、紅外線都有害<br />\n<br />\n讀得書少唔識就唔好扮識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>反射幾多<br />\n咁就要睇你嗰下地下係乜嘢地喇<br />\n沙地？石屎地？草地？泥地？<br />\n你又可以一口咬定10%嘅<br />\n<br />\n就當真係10%<br />\n仲有你附近d嘢<br />\nd車呀建築物呀泥呀沙呀水呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你咪擔遮囉<br />\n<br />\n我冇話淨係得uv有害<br />\n但d師奶港女的確淨係識uv</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">concrete reflect about 8%-12% and asphalt about 4%-8%. </span>  Even soil reflects between 4%-6% and grass about 2%-5%.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.uvdaily.com.au/blog/reflected-uv/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uvdaily.com.au%2Fblog%2Freflected-uv%2F&d=i4R458lrHm%2FInVyxz36gUNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=2e2e1512\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.uvdaily.com.au/blog/reflected-uv/</a><br />\n<br />\n就算塗滿白色嘅建築物係20% 呢啲google下就搵到 <br />\n城市你同我講有水 邊個會係水入面擔遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n你自己行上街問下擔遮嘅師奶港女<br />\n係因為曬 燦眼先擔遮 定係因為防UV<br />\n<br />\n邏輯真係&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪死雞撐飯蓋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T13:34:02.000Z","msg":"全新白包石屎56% 但只要唔係白色relective index就會大跌 計埋其他街上面有既平面都不出10% 所以當平均10~20%好合理<br />\n而且計皮膚接觸到幾多光唔係10%+12%咁加曬佢 而係要平均數 因為計緊每單位皮膚受光<br />\n唔理把遮防唔防UV 擔遮都擋左大部分熱能先 所以擔遮唔係問題 問題係把遮插到人果啲仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">為左樓主用曬中文黎寫</span></span>"}]}